author: sascharodekamp
msg: FIX: Missing UiLabel and typos on Anonymous Checkout (https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/OFBIZ-4414) A patch from Carsten Schinzer: custsetting.ftl has typos: Opening tag <lable> is used on four occasions instead of <label> while closing tags correctly refer to </label>. Header of section refers to EcommerceUiLabel "EcommerceYourNamePhoneAndEmail" which is not present in specialpurpose/ecommerce/config/EcommerceUiLabels.xml.
